OL,3,C'Lives could be lost' due to Llanelli
OL,4,Cminor injuries unit cuts, campaigners
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,F"Lives could be lost" in Llanelli due
OL,8,Fto cuts to the town's minor injuries
OL,9,Funit.
OL,11,FThat's the verdict from campaigners
OL,12,Fwho are worried by moves to close the
OL,13,Fservice at the town's hospital at
OL,14,Fnight for the next six months.
OL,16,FThe health board insists it can't
OL,17,Fsustain the service due to staffing
OL,18,Fchallenges.
