OL,3,C'Lives could be lost' due to Llanelli
OL,4,Cminor injuries unit cuts, campaigners
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,FThe unit which is usually open 24
OL,8,Fhours a day will now be closed between
OL,9,F8pm to 8am from November 1, for six
OL,10,Fmonths.
OL,12,FClinical lead Jon Morris said: "To
OL,13,Fensure the safety and confidence of
OL,14,Fpeople attending the minor injury
OL,15,Funit, we need to able to provide a fit
OL,16,Ffor purpose service during all opening
OL,17,Fhours.
