OL,3,C'Lives could be lost' due to Llanelli
OL,4,Cminor injuries unit cuts, campaigners
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,F"The inability to consistently cover
OL,8,Fthe rota, with suitably qualified
OL,9,Fdoctors, particularly during the
OL,10,Fevenings and overnight, carries risk
OL,11,Fto our patients and our staff, with
OL,12,Fstaff absences then compounding the
OL,13,Fproblem."
OL,15,FHywel Dda University Health Board has
OL,16,Fdetailed its problems securing
OL,17,Fsuitably-qualified doctors to provide
OL,18,Fcover in the MIU. Between February
OL,19,F2024 and July 2024, there were 42
OL,20,Funcovered slots, in which 23 were the
OL,21,Fovernight shift.
