OL,3,C'Lives could be lost' due to Llanelli
OL,4,Cminor injuries unit cuts, campaigners
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,FAndrew Carruthers, the health board's
OL,8,Fchief operating officer, said: "As we
OL,9,Fapproach winter it's really important
OL,10,Fthat we have a clinical model that is
OL,11,Fsafe.
OL,13,F"Failure to take action will lead to
OL,14,Fmore staff leaving and could leave the
OL,15,Fdaytime service fragile."
OL,17,FMore than 15,000 people have signed a
OL,18,Fpetition which has been handed to
OL,19,Fhospital management. Some campaigners
OL,20,Fare even camping outside of the
OL,21,Fhospital.
