OL,3,C'Lives could be lost' due to Llanelli
OL,4,Cminor injuries unit cuts, campaigners
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,FOne of them is Andrew Bragoli who says
OL,8,Fstaff at the hospital saved his life
OL,9,Fwhen he suffered a stroke in work.
OL,11,FHe said: "When you have a stroke, it's
OL,12,Fthe first ten minutes that is vital to
OL,13,Fget (treatment). I work in Tata Steel,
OL,14,Fwhich is no more than a mile way from
OL,15,Fhere.
OL,17,F"The minor injury unit probably saved
OL,18,Fme. Once (the new opening times are)
OL,19,Fput in place, the precedent is set and
OL,20,Fthat will be it."
