OL,3,C'Lives could be lost' due to Llanelli
OL,4,Cminor injuries unit cuts, campaigners
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,FHospital clinical director Robin
OL,8,FGhosal said: "Whilst this temporary
OL,9,Fchange is in place, it is important to
OL,10,Fstress that Prince Philip Hospital
OL,11,Fcontinues to provide acute medical
OL,12,Fcare for the local population. These
OL,13,Fcases come into the unit via ambulance
OL,14,For via GP referral. We will work
OL,15,Fclosely with GPs and the Welsh
OL,16,FAmbulance Services Trust to ensure
OL,17,Fthese patients continue to be seen in
OL,18,FPrince Philip Hospital, as their
OL,19,Fclosest hospital."
